<para id="import-auto-id2661605"> Repeat the previous problem for the situation in which the rocket sled decelerates at a rate of <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msup><m:mtext>01 m/s</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. In this problem, the forces are exerted by the seat and restraining belts.</para>
